a0d57d362d375e8d4ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClare%20Brown's%20family%20first%20moved%20to%20Florida%20and%20then%20to%20Alabama.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Clare%20Brown%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20England%2C%20family%20and%20friends%20would%20have%20Freddie%20for%20a%20few%20hours%20so%20I%20could%20work%2C%20or%20for%20a%20sleepover%20so%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20could%20go%20on%20a%20date.%20We%20didn't%20have%20that%20anymore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChristmas%20and%20Easter%2C%20when%20my%20family%20would%20gather%2C%20are%20the%20times%20I%20missed%2C%20and%20continue%20to%20miss%2C%20my%20family%20most.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20a%20priority%20for%20me%20to%20speak%20to%20them%20once%20a%20week%20and%20fly%20back%20home%20to%20see%20them%20once%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20both%20ways%2C%20I%20stay%20connected%20to%20them%20even%20though%20we%20are%20an%20ocean%20away.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22adfc11a4-d9e0-4238-a92b-1fa6e9f9f143%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20worried%20about%20our%20aging%20parents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20my%20biggest%20worry%20is%20how%20we%20will%20care%20for%20our%20aging%20parents.%20My%20dad%20died%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20I%20only%20just%20made%20it%20home%20in%20time%20to%20say%20goodbye.%20His%20death%20made%20me%20realize%20how%20fast%20death%20can%20happen%2C%20and%20consider%20how%20we'll%20support%20our%20families%20from%20afar%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20silver%20lining%20in%20being%20so%20far%20from%20extended%20family%20has%20been%20that%20our%20family%20unit%20of%20three%20does%20everything%20together%20and%20has%20become%20incredibly%20close%20because%20of%20it.%20Not%20surrounded%20by%20other%20family%2C%20we%20depend%20on%20each%20other%20in%20a%20way%20we%20wouldn't%20have%20if%20we%20lived%20back%20in%20England.%3C%2Fspan%3E%