they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221d502dd3-a155-4f09-8375-3c4fc39117fb%5C%22%3EPushing%20for%20too%20much%20information%20at%20once%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223793%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20sitting%20across%20from%20each%20other%20at%20a%20table.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dc283b1c1f80efbec49f4d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222845%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20first%20date%20should%20be%20an%20easygoing%20interaction.%3Cp%3E10'000%20Hours%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBethany%20Skorik%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-wedding-guests-should-never-make-etiquette-coach-tips%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eetiquette%20coach%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20founder%20of%20Ascent%20Etiquette%20and%20Communications%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it's%20important%20to%20remember%20that%20a%20first%20date%20isn't%20an%20interview.%20This%20means%20you%20likely%20won't%20learn%20everything%20about%20a%20person%20in%20one%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20she%20said%20the%20initial%20date%20should%20be%20an%20easygoing%20interaction%20and%20shouldn't%20pry%20too%20deeply%20into%20someone's%20personal%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFocus%20on%20assessing%20the%20person's%20energy%2C%20hobbies%2C%20and%20general%20outlook%20on%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Skorik%20said.%20%26quot%3BMost%20people%20aren't%20comfortable%2C%20or%20obligated%2C%20to%20share%20information%20about%20their%20family%20life%2C%20finances%2C%20ex-lovers%2C%20or%20personal%20back%20story%20with%20a%20stranger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22085aa72d-7505-47d4-8f5f-eed08e858bad%5C%22%3EMaking%20a%20mess%20at%20dinner%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224776%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20basket%20of%20chicken%20wings%20with%20sauce.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68dc28675dbc4fd10da9e1