blic%20companies%20in%20the%20US%20that%20operate%20with%20dual%20CEOs%2C%20according%20to%20the%20analytics%20firm%20Boardroom%20Alpha.%20Yet%20the%20setup%20is%20having%20a%20moment%3A%20In%20little%20more%20than%20a%20week%2C%20Spotify%2C%20Comcast%2C%20and%20Oracle%20have%20recently%20announced%20that%20they%20will%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspotify-comcast-oracle-announce-co-ceo-model-leadership-bet-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eco-CEOs%20lead%20their%20organizations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20getting%20bogged%20down%20by%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epotential%20risks%20of%20partnerships%20%E2%80%94%20uneven%20power%20splits%2C%20fuzzy%20accountability%2C%20or%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Estrategic%20clashes%20%E2%80%94%20some%20companies%20are%20embracing%20the%20idea%20that%2C%20in%20a%20period%20when%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femad-mostaque-elon-musk-being-a-ceo-sucks-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEOs'%20remits%20are%20broader%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20ever%2C%20more%20can%20be%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20really%20has%20allowed%20us%20to%20specialize%20in%20the%20things%20that%20we're%20respectively%20passionate%20about%20and%20great%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20Mike%20Sobel%2C%20co-CEO%20of%20fintech%20company%20Trumid%2C%20said%20of%20the%20division%20of%20labor%20he%20has%20with%20his%20counterpart%2C%20Ronnie%20Mateo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227af75c56-68c0-4a2c-aae0-3b727b7e5d43%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnowing%20who%20does%20what%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESobel%20joined%20Trumid%20in%202014%2C%20when%20the%20startup%20was%20about%20five%20months%20old.%20For%20years%20after%2C%20he%20and%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20colleagues%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20bond%20traders%20and%20salespeople%20with%20experience%20from%20across%20Wall%20Street%20%E2%80%94%20worked%20alongside%20Mateo%20to%20build%20a%20fixed-income%20platform.%20In