d%20you'll%20find%20a%20community%20that%20follows.%20I'd%20been%20posting%20my%20progress%20on%20X%2C%20where%20I%20have%20about%208%2C000%20followers%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewhich%20attracted%20the%20interest%20of%20some%20venture%20capitalists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20finally%2C%20be%20delusional!%20You've%20got%20to%20be%20this%20infectiously%20positive%20person%20who%20is%20obsessed%20with%20what%20they're%20creating.%20If%20you're%20doing%20something%20your%20curiosity%20found%20for%20you%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20make%20cash%2C%20in%20my%20mind%2C%20that's%20the%20way%20to%20become%20successful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteen-dropped-out-school-after-raising-funds-ai-project-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1759570621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d6555b5dbc4fd10da9a007%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteen-dropped-out-school-after-raising-funds-ai-project-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Toby%20Brown%2C%2016%2C%20raised%20%241%20million%20for%20his%20AI%20project%2C%20Beem.%20He%20dropped%20out%20of%20school%20in%20the%20UK%20to%20pursue%20the%20project%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzitser%40businessinsider.com%20(Joshua%20Nelken-Zitser)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteen-dropped-out-school-after-raising-funds-ai-project-2025-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Irregularities%20In%20Sabarimala%20Temple's%20Gold%20Plating%20Sparks%20Political%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20controversy%20over%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20gold%20plating%20of%20the%20Sabarimala%20temple%20sanctum%20has%20snowballed%20into%20a%20political%20issue%2C%20as%20the%20Travancore%20Devaswom%20Board%20said%20ther