%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20chasing%20what%20we%20saw%20in%20that%20movie%20Avatar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20reconnect%20with%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20acquiring%20the%20land%2C%20which%20was%20then%20covered%20in%20a%20eucalyptus%20forest%20%E2%80%94%20a%20non-native%20species%20%E2%80%94%20the%20major%20challenge%20was%20rewilding%20it.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20land%20was%20used%20for%20agricultural%20purposes%2C%20it%20had%20been%20flattened%20and%20had%20some%205%2C000%20eucalyptus%20trees.%20These%20trees%20would%20dry%20up%20the%20groundwater%20and%20wetlands%20as%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20belong%20to%20this%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Jai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20biosphere%20was%20created%20through%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20of%20relentless%20effort.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-500x374.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-768x575.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-1536x1150.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frajaji4-1724833594-150x112.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-363168%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20biosphere%20was%20created%20through%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years%20of%20relentless%20effort.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%20and%20Vijay%20surveyed%20the%20nearby%20area%20of%20the%20Rajaji%20Tiger%20Reserve%20and%20National%20Park%20together%2C%20identifying%2062%20native%20tree%20species%20that%20were%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20disappearing.%20The%20project%20began%20with%20the%20collection%20of%20seeds%20and%20the%20painstaking%20process%20of%20planting%20saplings%20of%20these%20endangered%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijay%2C%20who%20has%20been%20in%20the%20rewilding%20and%20wildlife%20restoration%20space%20for%20over%2020%20years%20and%20majorly%20works%20on%20government%20projects%2C%20had%20an%20interesting%20task%20up%20his%20sleeve.%20He%20states%20that%20there%20is%20just%20a%20wall%20that%20separates%20the%20biosphere%20from%20the%20Rajaji%20National%20Park.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20get%20a%20slice%20of%20Rajaji%20into%20this%20land%2C%20which%20had%20been%20altered%20by%20humans%20for%20their%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20task%20was%20removing%20the%20eucalyptus%20trees.%20The%20second%20task%20was%20creating%20natural%20contours%20that%20existed%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20monsoon%20that%20I%20experienced%20was%20really%20horrifying.%20I%20found%20that%20the%20rainwater%20was%20tapering%20away%20towards%20the%20river.%20Nothing%20was%20being%20retained%20in%20the%20land.%20The%20rain%20was%20taking%20away%20my%20topsoil%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vijay%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20a%20war%20footing%2C%20we%20created%20the%20natural%20contours%20that%20existed%20to%20ensure%20that%20rainwater%20recharges%20our%20land.%20We%20are%20working%20on%20creating%20magic%2C%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20they%20worked%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345145%2Fforest-officer-saves-trees-in-chhattisgarh-forest-tiger-res