t%20on%20to%20utilise%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreader%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoter.%20%E2%80%9CInsect%20thrips%20damage%20the%20buds%20and%20leaves%20of%20crops.%20I%20once%20mixed%20aloe%20vera%20with%20fish%20oil%20and%20sprayed%20it%20on%20crops.%20Pests%20and%20animals%20dislike%20it%20because%20of%20its%20bitter%20taste.%20I%20found%20this%20to%20be%20an%20effective%20pest%20repellent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hrushikesh%20utilises%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreader%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Faloe-vera-1-1723014094-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360103%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHrushikesh%20uses%20aloe%20vera%20to%20make%20natural%20pesticides%2C%20herbal%20spreaders%2C%20and%20plant%20growth%20promoters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CPlants%20like%20bananas%20naturally%20avert%20water%20on%20its%20surface.%20It%20becomes%20difficult%20for%20farmers%20to%20spray%20pesticides%20on%20their%20leaves.%20Spraying%2