2wp-image-364806%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%20At%20least%2015%2C000%20small-landholding%20farmers%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20are%20reaping%20the%20benefits%20of%20biofortified%20seeds.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%205%20(2019-21)%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1795421%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E57%20percent%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20women%20aged%2015-49%20in%20India%20are%20anaemic%20whereas%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1806601%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E35.5%20percent%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20children%20under%20five%20years%20of%20age%20are%20stunted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAishwarya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20untapped%20power%20in%20the%20food%20we%20consume%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20our%20diet%20is%20%3Cem%3Eroti%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20rice.%20Looking%20at%20the%20anaemia%20and%20stunting%20data%20of%20our%20country%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20we%20do%20not%20get%20enough%20nutrients%20from%20the%20food%20we%20eat.%20I%20strongly%20believe%20that%20nutrition%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20luxury%20but%20a%20right%20for%20us%20all%20Indians.%20It%E2%80%99s%20something%20everyone%20deserves%20access%20to%2C%20and%20cannot%20be%20a%20privilege%20for%20a%20few.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERealising%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20improve%20crop%20nutrition%20naturally%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20fortify%20seeds%20of%20crops%20such%20as%20maize%2C%20paddy%2C%20wheat%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296561%2Fmahalingam-govindaraj-scientist-develops-first-biofortified-pearl-millet-bajra